OOC: Gotcha.

"Okey dokey, let's get this crate open."  Wheeljack-X retracts one of 
his hands and one of his vast assortment of electronic devices pops 
out of his wrist socket.  He uses it to send a signal to the ship's 
systems, opening the main hatch by remote.
